{"tid":679054,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"條魚骨插咗入牙縫...想死...","createTime":"2018-05-26T14:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T02:20:11.000Z","uid":110895,"like":207,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"e71fdfeb1ad88bfde960a1449eba3f4da440b14a","tid":679054,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"就係啲死人魚青...<br />\n連骨打...<br />\n條碎骨直插入上顎牙縫...重要係最後果2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牙籤牙刷油/水浪口...用勻都冇效(屋企冇醋...唔係試埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n開始重見到條骨的尖尖(用手機照)<br />\n然後試用眉鋏夾佢。連個尖喙都冇埋...(應該係插入咗)<br />\n<br />\n幾個鍾了...點算...<br />\n唔係話好痛...但好唔舒服<br />\n想死...好似我當年AL考衰咗...第一份工比人炒咁失落...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚重要冇醫生...醫院排到通宵都得...私家又好貴...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明天重要日文考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(其實溫得8899...不過未做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有妙法..."},{"pid":"521f587e0087a55272092cfd5814721a4f2dfdc5","tid":679054,"uid":23445,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:25:23.000Z","msg":"牙線"},{"pid":"17b97fe0d49f6b400bb27b99fbc0e49b4b3db995","tid":679054,"uid":46943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"屌你牙線"},{"pid":"844e0bbdcc35cd4fbb95b2cb63bf18e805080f0f","tid":679054,"uid":32937,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"牙縫刷"},{"pid":"989fe65e0f7c692968ecdac6e2fabe3924c254c6","tid":679054,"uid":76526,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e71fdfeb1ad88bfde960a1449eba3f4da440b14a","tid":679054,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"就係啲死人魚青...<br />\n連骨打...<br />\n條碎骨直插入上顎牙縫...重要係最後果2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cla